snippet.title: Cotton 100% - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
🔮 Something magical has arrived! 🔮
Cotton 100% offers beautiful and charming cute 'em up side-scrolling action from the 90s!Cotton and Silk head out to save the world...and eat some tasty Willows. 🌈 Newly resurrected magical adventures for your Nintendo Switch & PS4, available digitally, right now!


For more info, check out: https://www.iningames.com/games/cotton-100/
